Package: federalregister.gov
Title: Federal Register API Client for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Federal Register API. Search
    documents, executive orders, rules, proposed rules, agencies, and public
    inspection documents. All functions return tibbles.
